tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE conflict_resolution_strategies(
    strategy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_name VARCHAR(255),
    success_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
    total_attempts INT,
    successful_attempts INT
)
CREATE TABLE conflict_resolution_strategies (id INT, strategy_name VARCHAR(255), success_rate DECIMAL(5,2))
CREATE TABLE conflict_data (id INT, strategy_id INT, date_inserted TIMESTAMP, outcome TEXT)
CREATE TABLE strategy_feedback (id INT, strategy_id INT, rating INT, comments TEXT)

CREATE TABLE ConflictResolutionStrategies (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  strategy_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  success_rate FLOAT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE ConflictData (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  strategy_id INT REFERENCES ConflictResolutionStrategies(id),
  date_collected DATE,
  outcome VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE ConflictParticipants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  strategy_id INT REFERENCES ConflictResolutionStrategies(id)
)

CREATE TABLE ConflictFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_id INT REFERENCES ConflictData(data_id),
  participant_id INT REFERENCES ConflictParticipants(participant_id),
  feedback_text TEXT
)
